with the contract.

153
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:00,920
Please check it.

154
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:03,200
Can't you guys solve the problem?

155
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,360
Why do you always bother me?

156
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,560
Losers!

157
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:06,440
Get out!

158
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:19,920
(How to find biological parents?)

159
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,080
Gu Yibei,

160
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,200
I found you at last.

161
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,520
Where have you been these days?

162
