169
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,520
I'm OK with that.

170
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,640
But honestly,

171
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,360
when you were away,

172
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,760
I contacted the suppliers

173
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:52,280
and negotiated with the contractors.

174
00:08:52,280 --> 00:08:54,080
(How to find biological parents?)
Even a little problem with the Technical Dept.

175
00:08:54,640 --> 00:08:56,840
I was as busy as a bee.

176
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:59,000
You have to take me out

177
00:08:59,000 --> 00:08:59,960
